text: Shoghakat may also refer to: * Shoghakat Church, Vagharshapat (Etchmiadzin), Armavir Province, Armenia * Shoghakat Church of Tabriz, East Azerbaijan Province, Iran * Shoghakat, Armenia, a village on Lake Sevan, Gegharkunik Province, Armenia * Shoghakat TV, an Armenian television channel based in Yerevan, Armenia
